<BaseLayout title="How to Use Camera Angles" description="Use camera angle and framing terms in AI image prompts." canonicalPath="/guides/camera-angles/"><article class="content-section article-body"><h1>How to Use Camera Angles in AI Images</h1><p>Camera words decide what the viewer sees first. Choose close-up for faces, full body for outfit design, wide shot for environments, low angle for drama, and high angle for layout clarity.</p><p>Pick one main framing idea. Combining wide shot and close-up in the same prompt often creates a confused composition.</p></article></BaseLayout>
